text: have 3 kids. 1st didnt really benefit much. but my other 2 kids did benefit from the daily work. this method may not suit all children. you just gotta test it out. what i like about this centre is the level of attention the give to my kids, such as how they sit, how they write, and their use of the audio tracks that helps my kids learn to pronounce words properly.
I have a bad experience on this branch with the principal. Not approachable and not professional.
